oMail - INSTALL
===============


* You will need:
  --------------
- qmail 1.03 (Dan Bernstein) 
  http://www.qmail.org

- vmailmgrd 0.96.7 (Bruce Guenter)    (didn't tried with any other versions)
  http://www.em.ca/~bruceg/vmailmgr/

- qmail-autoresponder (Bruce Guenter)   
  http://www.em.ca/~bruceg/qmail-autoresponder/

- php 4.0.x
  http://www.php.net

- apache 1.3.x
  http://www.apache.org/httpd.html



* Installation  (draft)
  ------------

  1. install qmail, autorespond and vmailmgr

  2. make sure vmailmgrd (the vmailmgr daemon) is running. Don't forget it needs uscpi-unix to work.
     ( /usr/local/bin/unixserver /tmp/.vmailmgrd vmailmgrd )

	* current version : vmailmgr 0.96.7 + daemon/autorespond.cc patch :

Index: autoresponse.cc
===================================================================
